{"tid":461682,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"胡鴻鈞深夜送外賣 上許廷鏗屋企留宿","createTime":"2017-11-08T01:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T22:55:24.000Z","uid":6604,"like":206,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"e045ec00c1e78a253ec535463a76ac61476166f4","tid":461682,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"歌手兼牙醫許廷鏗(Alfred)憑俊朗外型同磁性聲線冧掂唔少女性fans，同時多次傳出斷背緋聞，與「嫩版陳奐仁」公園瞓大髀及咀嘴，之後同關心妍嘅「易服男」助手阿小傳喺的士纏綿，又與張敬軒傳過緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n今日有周刊指，許廷鏗同胡鴻鈞關係亦係友達以上，之前許廷鏗係同屋企人一齊住，不過未知係唔係專心搞音樂，加上o依家做「華納一哥」，佢就搬咗去大圍，日前影到好友胡鴻鈞出完騷去買甜品同泰國菜送外賣上許廷鏗屋企，成程胡鴻鈞都戴上口罩，當晚更留喺許廷鏗屋企，成晚冇離開，報道又指平時許廷鏗同胡鴻鈞都係有影皆雙，不時喺Ig貼出合照，難怪傳出斷背情!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171107/large/1510025566_316f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171107%2Flarge%2F1510025566_316f.jpg&h=20051334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1794fb0d82f9975101bb3ea432916824e940cee4","tid":461682,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3490499cd90c0e0af136391db2354ac2836015f","tid":461682,"uid":21423,"like":60,"dislike":4,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:06:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffd0eecd5b106615b90d4d63919ed90ea350013e","tid":461682,"uid":35408,"like":27,"dislike":49,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fe7b9c3656ca3edc6a67a80fbd194975d2d28b","tid":461682,"uid":59886,"like":75,"dislike":11,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"Faggots"},{"pid":"b0fc2a49e37b1f113b8a1b140df1a1cb44a934fa","tid":461682,"uid":70391,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"欣宜呢"},{"pid":"eda4d44d7968765fa8fd98f2e9b0b781532ae257","tid":461682,"uid":12021,"